## Key Insight
Team-aware changes seem to HURT tournament performance despite helping locally.
The base policy's aggressive 5-pressure budget works well in tournament because
tournament matches are against OTHER alpha versions that also handle small teams
poorly. Being more conservative with team-size-aware budgets just means scoring
less when you have the numbers advantage (6v2).

## Next Steps
- Focus on what actually improves tournament: the simple aggressive base strategy
- Try uploading base + resource bias only (minimal changes from v65)
- Consider if v65's score is inflated by early weak-opponent matches
